  • Packages that use com.mgnt.lifecycle.management 
    Package Description
    com.mgnt.lifecycle.management.backgroundrunner
    This package contains infrastructure that can run user implemented Task classes in a separate thread at configured time interval.
    com.mgnt.lifecycle.management.backgroundrunner.example

    This package with all its subpackages contains a source code example that demonstrates how infrastructure in package com.mgnt.lifecycle.management should be used.
